    (E'590', E'Crews Hill Golf Club', E'Enfield', E'Cattlegate Road\n\nEnfield\n\nEN2 8AZ', E'This private members club admits diners who are also permitted to use the bar that overlooks miles of scenic countryside. Smart casual dress standards apply. Guest beer changes every few weeks.', 51.6839, -0.110312, E'(020) 8363 6674', E'https://placekitten.com/400/300'),
    (E'591', E'Cricketers', E'Enfield', E'19 Chase Side Place\n\nEnfield\n\nEN2 6QA', E'Hidden away off Chase Side, this pub is decorated inside and out with cricketing paraphernalia and memorabilia.', 51.6564, -0.0873086, E'(020) 8363 5218', E'https://placekitten.com/401/301'),
    (E'592', E'Crown & Horseshoes', E'Enfield', E'15 Horseshoe Lane\n\nEnfield\n\nEN2 6PZ', E'Picturesque canalside setting with a very large garden. Now re-branded  a GK Flamegrill by Greene King. Landlord has been given permission to buy outside the GK stable and currently has Redemption and Landlord as regulars along with GK IPA. His guest will come from GK.', 51.6559, -0.086995, E'(020) 8363 1371', E'https://placekitten.com/402/302'),
